---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RadixDialogExample from '../../components/RadixExample';
---

<Layout>
  <div id="root">
    <div class="flex flex-col h-dvh">
      <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto">
        <div>
          <div class="mx-auto relative sm:my-10 max-w-4xl">
            <div
              class="bg-surface-dimmed flex items-center flex-wrap justify-center gap-1 pt-2 pb-1 mx-0 sm:mx-10 font-semibold rounded-t border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-t sm:border-x border-surface-outline"
            >
              <a
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors underline underline-offset-2 text-link-base hover:text-link-hover"
                href="/"><span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">Lobby</span></a
              ><div class="shrink-0">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="16"
                  height="16"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="tabler-icon tabler-icon-slash"
                  ><path d="M17 5l-10 14"></path></svg
                >
              </div><a
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors underline underline-offset-2 text-link-base hover:text-link-hover"
                href="/design-system/"
                ><span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">Design System</span></a
              >
            </div><div
              class="relative bg-surface-base px-12 py-10 min-h-dvh sm:min-h-0 sm:border sm:border-surface-outline sm:rounded-lg sm:shadow-xl"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
                <div>
                  <div
                    class="text-content-accent text-lg md:text-2xl font-extrabold"
                  >
                    Radix UI Components
                  </div>
                </div><div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 mb-10">
                Radix UI provides unstyled, accessible components for building high-quality design systems. 
                These components are designed to integrate with Astro and can be styled using Tailwind CSS to match your application's design.
              </div>

              <h3 class="font-bold mt-8 text-lg text-content-accent">Dialog Component</h3>
              <p class="text-content-base text-sm mb-4">
                A modal dialog that interrupts the user with important content and expects a response.
              </p>
              <div class="p-4 border border-surface-outline rounded-lg mb-8 bg-surface-dimmed">
                <RadixDialogExample client:load />
                <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-surface-base rounded border border-surface-outline">
                  <p class="text-sm text-content-dimmed">
                    This dialog component uses Radix UI's unstyled primitives with Tailwind CSS for styling.
                    The dialog is accessible and follows WAI-ARIA design patterns.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <h3 class="font-bold mt-8 text-lg text-content-accent">Usage Notes</h3>
              <p class="text-content-base text-sm mb-4">
                Follow these steps to use Radix UI components in your Astro project.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 mt-2 mb-8">
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="font-bold text-content-accent">1.</div>
                  <div class="text-content-base">Import the component from the appropriate Radix UI package</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="font-bold text-content-accent">2.</div>
                  <div class="text-content-base">Use the component in your JSX/TSX files</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="font-bold text-content-accent">3.</div>
                  <div class="text-content-base">When using in Astro files, add the <code class="bg-surface-dimmed px-1 rounded text-content-accent">client:load</code> directive (or other client directives as needed)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="font-bold text-content-accent">4.</div>
                  <div class="text-content-base">Style with Tailwind CSS classes using the design system's semantic color names</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
